data.description: *** 2.79% VA Assumable Mortgage *** Welcome to this charming two-story, four-bedroom, 2.5-bath residence that boasts an array of desirable features for comfortable living. The cozy front porch invites relaxation and friendly neighborhood chats. Inside, an open concept living and dining room create an inviting space for gatherings. Kitchen duties will be a joy with the natural light pouring in from the large windows overlooking the serene backyard. The spacious master suite is large enough for an additional sitting area and has a double vanity and two closets for your convenience. Step outside onto the large deck, perfect for lounging, dining, and grilling out. Shading & ornamental trees surround the backyard for privacy and serenity. This home combines modern comforts with a warm, welcoming atmosphere, making it an ideal place to call your own.
